"One for the people, one for the parliament/
One for the weary, one for the malcontent/ 
One for the master, one for the protege/
One for you and one for me"

name: Merely's Web Slinger
description: Nobody slings web like Merely.  Nobody. Srsly.

name: Order of the Ruby Dragon
description: Protected by dragon hide and his brothers, he fears no man or beast.

name: Taco Launcher
description: It's raining tacos! Not really- more like you're shooting tacos. Fire tacos at your friends and foes. If hit they will take 20 damage as they eat the taco.  Occasionally there is a very spicy taco that will turn the eater bright red!

name: Hat-Eating Hat
description: My hat can beat up your hat.

name: Trashy Hat
description: Anyone ever call you trashy? If I saw you in this hat, I probably would too.

name: Purple Shaggy
description: Because lime green shaggys don't understand sarcasm.

name: Beach Ball Head
description: There is only beach ball now.

name: Diamond Blade Sword
description: What cuts like diamond? Nothing. Swing this super powerful sword over your head.  As it sparkles around you, the sword does powerful damage to your foe. If you manage to blox them, they will turn into a diamond as they fall apart.

name: Cookie Clicker Crown
description: You clicked the cookie!

name: SFOTH IV Crown of Fire
description: Some people are afraid of sword fighting. Some people are afraid of heights. Some people are afraid of fire. Those people are babies.

name: Spiked Fedora
description: Because sometimes you look at a hat and think - "Man, that hat seems too comfortable.  I'd really like it better if there were spikes!"

name: Jade Warrior
description: On the verge of exile, the jade warrior fights with all the might of the universe to prove the worth of the Jade Clan.

name: Blackvalk Shades
description: For when you're ridin'... but it's dark.

name: Tiger's Wrath Sword
description: ROAR!  Attack your foes with the speed of a tiger. If you are able to slay 5 foes with this mighty sword, you will be able to use its special Tiger Raig attack- which lets you slash over and over again and creates a red danger circle that will do damage to anyone within it.

name: Wolf Knight
description: "A man might befriend a wolf, even break a wolf, but no man could truly tame a wolf."

name: Gentleman Penguin
description: Why should gentility be only for humans?  Penguins can be sophisticated too!

name: Orinthian Cape
description: The strength required to fly in battle is great.  This cape helps the Orinthians with flight while they fight.

name: Red Glowing Eyes
description: You're watching Amazon Prime videos- just chillin' on a typical Friday night. You hear a sound. You look out the window. You see these red glowing eyes and nothing else.  You go out side to inspect the situation. You approach the figure. It is your best friend. He bought this face just to mess with you. Friends are weird.

name: Skull of Robloxians Past
description: "The fear of death follows from the fear of life. A man who lives fully is prepared to die at any time."  This item came out of the Gift of Robloxians Past on October 8th, 2014.

name: All Hallow's Sword
description: Slash at your foes and deal 15 damage per hit.  If you're looking to do something a little more interesting - hit 'Q' to grow vines that will stun and trap anyone within a 15 stud radius.  The 'E' key will shoot 10 vines in front of you to hit your opponents - doing  12 damage. Finally - press the 'X' key  to activate a vine like shield, which arises from the ground and surrounds you for 20 seconds. It does 20 damage to anyone who runs into it.

name: Scary Bloxxing Pumpkin
description: Creepy pumpkins lurk about all Bloxtober long!

name: Abraham Dusek
description: 1 part Dusek + 1 part Lincoln = 100% speed + 100% freedom = 200% awesome!

name: Oceanic Guard Helmet
description: The Oceanic Guard are an elite squad of men chosen to protect the Prince of the Seas.

name: Telamax XR71 Shoulder Cannon
description: The Telemax XR71 Shoulder Cannon is a vital piece in every soldier's arsenal.  Shoot your enemies and revitalize yourself!

name: Gadgetron 2700
description: Whatever you need, Gadgetron's got you covered.  Unless you need a cookie.  There is no room in Gadgetron for cookies.  Cookies are not gadgets.

name: Brighteyes' Summer Vacation Leftovers
description: Summer's over, but Brighteyes still has some summer hats.  Who doesn't love leftovers? Interrupting starfish for the win!

name: Winged Helm of the Northern Brothers
description: They move so fast it feels like they're flying.

name: Poison Horns
description: Probably not a smart idea to make see through compartments for the poison in your hat.

name: Sheriff Wilson
description: ROBLOX is full of cowboys.  Sheriff Wilson keeps them in line (and testing their code on the test site).

name: Ghostfire Dagger

name: Sword of Ancalagon

name: A Dark Omen

name: Dark Dragon Lord

name: Azurewrath: Lord of the Frost

"To die, to sleep— /
To sleep—perchance to dream. / Ay, there's the rub!/
For in that sleep of death what dreams may come, /
When we have shuffled off this mortal coil"

name: Spec Zeta Biograft Energy Sword
description: After the tremendous success of the Epsilon sword, only one person was left who understood how to make energy swords.  This is largely due to the scientists testing the swords on one another in an effort to create the best product possible (and to keep all the profit for themselves).  The last scientist left standing created only 200 of these before he was spawn killed by a noob holding his own sword.

name: Zeus's Lightning Bolt Staff
description: Hurl lightning at your enemies.  Because they probably deserve it.

name: Annoying Elf: Ostrichsized

description: Make it snow everywhere you go!

name: Humbug Tie
description: Bah Humbug.

description: Wrath of the gods. And those ancient Egyptian gods were pretty wrathful.

name: Metal Horus

name: Greenbot
description: Greenbot only wants the earth to be green. Unfortunately, the humans have to go!

name: The First Time I Ever Played ROBLOX...
description: So when I joined ROBLOX in June 2006, we had just released multiplayer games. Back then we had 0 players. When a player logged in, the whole office would stop working to get in game to make sure (s)he had someone to play with. We even considered hiring a high school kid to play ROBLOX all summer as a job.

name: Fuchsia Kitty Ears
description: No kitties where harmed in the making of these ears. We couldn't find any real fuchsia kitties, so we had to make them out of fabric.

name: Hat of the Week: Year of the Tiger Dragon
description: Is Tiger-Dragon a new species?  No.  It's the Year of the Tiger.  This Dragon is celebrating the Year of the Tiger, but that's too long for a hat name.

description: She stole the tarts.

description: “You can never conquer the mountain. You can only conquer yourself.”

name: Blue Mardi Gras Mask
description: Popular practices included wearing masks and costumes, overturning social conventions, dancing, sports competitions, parades, etc. Similar expressions to Mardi Gras appear in other European languages sharing the Christian tradition. In English, the day is called Shrove Tuesday, associated with the religious requirement for confession before Lent begins.

name: Red Mardi Gras Mask
description: Mardi Gras is French for "Fat Tuesday" (in ethnic English tradition, Shrove Tuesday), referring to the practice of the last night of eating richer, fatty foods before the ritual fasting of the Lenten season, which started on Ash Wednesday. Related popular practices were associated with celebrations before the fasting and religious obligations associated with the penitential season of Lent.

description: Help Ultraman defeat his evil nemesis, Dr. Sinister Insight!

name: ): Gold Ollie
description: ): Ad campaigns of the late 1990's focused on the "Golden Moment" - that 7 seconds of air time you get going out of a half pipe at 80 mph. This is your Golden Moment.

name: Spec Epsilon Biograft Energy Sword
description: The superintelligent cloud people of the distant future find the history of human conflict hilarious and ironic. To that end, they created these weapons to sell in museum gift shops as a living reminder of the pinnacle of human stupidity. (WHY DO YOU NEED HAND TO HAND WEAPONS WHEN YOU HAVE LAZORS?!) Because the cloud people are incorporeal, the swords are completely harmless and they allow their young to play with them.

description:
Uncle Sean wants YOU to go read Easter, 1916. 
Now and in time to be, /
Wherever green is worn, /
Are changed, changed utterly: /
A terrible beauty is born.

name: Telamon's Crafting Jewel
description: So when I think about what ROBLOX features might be fun to implement one day, I usually think *really* far ahead. In the distant future, I think it might be fun to have a crafting system on ROBLOX, where you can combine items to create other items. If it ever happens, this jewel will be the key ingredient you need to create something awesome. If it never happens, well then this is just a spiky golden ball of broken dreams. - Telamon

HAD I the heavens’ embroidered cloths, /

The blue and the dim and the dark cloths /
Of night and light and the half light, /
I would spread the cloths under your feet: /
But I, being poor, have only my dreams; /
I have spread my dreams under your feet; /
Tread softly because you tread on my dreams. [Egg2010]

Magical Rainbow Pony fell out of the Pinata on 4/30/2010 at 4:10 PDT.

name: United Kingdom Hat

name: LOLHOW
description:
This strange fruit is eaten mostly by noobs but sometimes even by veteran Robloxians. The question on their minds is HOW? No really, how?! 

This hat came out of Reese's Mystery Pony Pinata on April 16,2010 at 10:50 PM PDT.

name: Flower Power
description: Roses are red, violets are blue, this hat is awesome, and so are you (if you are wearing this hat)!

name: Dr. Elephant
description: The elephant will see you now.

name: Alien Death Panda
description: ADP was sent from the future to scare us into saving the pandas!  Apparently, he did a good job because there are pandas in the future to send back to warn us.  Unless he isn't really a panda at all...

name: Captain's Flintlock
description: This flintlock is slightly more accurate than the average pirate's flintlock.  It's gold plated so the captain knows if any of the other pirates try to switch flintlocks with him while he's sleeping.

name: Thunderdrone
description: Thunderdrones engage in fierce battles with Lightningdrones.  For this reason, they must have a helmet that protects their head completely.

name: Noramros the Hero's Hero
description: Noramros works creating weapons for other heroes and thus helps them save others.  Of course dealing with narcissistic heroes all day can be a dangerous job, so he has to stay sharp... and have a fierce looking helmet.  No one knows what his actual face looks like....

name: Golden Gate Bridge
description: Or GG Bridge. As we call it.

name: Red Monster League Baseball Cap
description: You ain't in the sticks no more. This is the big time. Monster League Baseball.

name: Guardia Helm
description: Radius speaks of Guardia as if it were still a sovereign nation.

name: Warthulu
description: "Many ask: When will I rise again, to lay waste to all the pitiful creatures of Earth? I had been thinking about next Tuesday, but I'm booked on Oprah that day."

name: The Crown of Roses
description: The Crown of Roses is the traditional adornment of the High Priestess of the 47 Druid Orders who make their home in the far Western Wilds of Robloxia. Special care is taken to use only roses with the sharpest thorns; this is a crown no one wears lightly.

name: Sinister P.
description: In ROBLOXia, Sinister P. carves YOU.

name: Ruby Serpent Mummy Mask
description: The shriveled brown eye sees only in the past, but the Ruby eyes are firmed fixed upon the Eternal.

name: Uncle Zom's Hat
description: I want you... And your supple, delicious brains...

name: Pumpkin Bucket
description: It's in the "Horror" genre because it can hold a horrifyingly large amount of candy. Nomnomnom!

name: Hollywood Sign
description: Hollywood. The seat of American culture.

name: Bat Knight Bat Sword
description: You would think that you wouldn't need to use the word "Bat" so many times to name a sword.

name: Korblox Chosen
description: Life in the Korblox lands is not lived, but rather forged. The icy Great North has long since beat weakness out of the Korblox tribes, and the merely strong have been culled over millenia of constant conflict. Thus the Korblox are a mighty race. Individuals who seek to lead the Korblox armies must prove their prowess by making a journey deep under the ice to the Burned Lands and return to present a living ruby to the clan Deathspeaker. Many do not return. But those who do are marked as Chosen.

name: Sand Tempest Nomad
description: When you say "dancing" you mean prancing around. When he says "dancing" he means sticking pointy pieces of metal in people.

name: Fire Ruby Crest
description: Living rubies, snatched at great peril from the realm of the Korblox.

name: Goldbot Goldbot
description: His real name is supposed to just be "Goldbot", but programmers are often off by 1.

name: Hot Spot
description: Wearing this hat will put you in the hot spot. And it will be...uncomfortably hot.

name: Commando Skullcap
description: It's time to blox noobs and chew bubblegum... and I'm all out of gum.

name: Liberty Bell
description: Let Freedom Ring!

name: Eyes of Azurewrath
description: What terrible secrets hide behind those eyes?

name: The Awe Star
description: Awe... SNAP! As of November 13, 2009 there are exactly equal numbers of Awe Stars and Ninja Masks of Awesomeness in existence. If you combine both items, the Awe Star becomes a weapon of Ninjitsu domination!

name: Mr. Hatbot
description: His sole purpose is to fetch your other hats. It's demeaning but sometimes the truth hurts.

name: Black Crisis
description: If countless investing books have taught me anything, it is that in Chinese, Crisis and Opprotunity are represented by the same character. This character, however, only represents Crisis.

name: Crimson Katana of the Unsetting Sun
description: If not for victory and honor, then what?

name: Niagara Falls
description: “From a drop of water a logician could infer the possibility of an Atlantic or a Niagara without having seen or heard of one or the other.”

name: Disintergrex Blast Gun
description: Veteran space pirates swear by these, though they are hard to find these days. Manufactured specifically to combat robots in the War of the Second Uprising, the Disintergrex uses patented tri-pulse technology. Thus the hugely successful marketing slogan: "If it's still moving, shoot it three times!"

name: Apple Pie
description: I know banana cream is the traditional comedy throwing pie. I know that. But people don't eat banana cream pie for Thanksgiving, unless they work in a comedy factory and get them for free. Careful, the apples are hot!

name: Gobble Gobble
description: Win this by bringing the most turkeys back to the dinner table in the ROBLOX Thanksgiving Turkey Hunt!!!

name: Cleopatra
description: The face that sank a thousand ships.

name: Evil Vizer
description: If the skull on his hat doesn't tip you off, maybe you deserve to lose your kingdom.

name: Headdress of Aken-Aten, the Sun King
description: Akhenaten (pronounced /ˌɑːkəˈnɑːtən/; often also spelled Echnaton, Akhnaton, or rarely Ikhnaton; meaning Effective spirit of Aten) was known before the fifth year of his reign as Amenhotep IV (sometimes given its Greek form, Amenophis IV, and meaning Amun is Satisfied). A Pharaoh of the Eighteenth dynasty of Egypt, he ruled for 17 years and died in 1336 BC or 1334 BC. He is especially noted for abandoning traditional Egyptian polytheism and introducing worship centered on the Aten, which is sometimes described as monotheistic; but henotheism would be a more accurate description, since he ranked the Aten above other gods but did not deny their existence. Indeed, an early inscription likens them to stars as compared with the sun, and later official language avoids calling the Aten a god, as if to create for the solar deity a status above mere gods.

name: The Viper Band
description: The ancient Egyptians considered the serpent to be a sacred symbol: it can be seen in the tip of the crown which the Pharaoh, king of Egypt, used to wear.

name: Sci-Fi Santa
description: Sci-Fi Santa delivers presents to every child in the galaxy simultaneously using a device powered by exotic matter that uses tremendous amounts of energy to reverse-instance the physical space under trees to be a single location where gifts can easily be deposited.

name: Sports Santa
description: He refs the Reindeer Games, and sometimes enjoys kickboxing with the elves.

name: Golden Katana of the Unflinching Dawn
description: "Victory is reserved for those who are willing to pay it's price." - Sun Tzu

name: Diademed Barbarian Prince
description: Imma let you finish. But Kubla Khan was the best diademed barbarian prince of all time. Of all times.

name: Adventure Santa
description: Anyone can wrestle an alligator, but this guy can win. Not that you would be likely to find an alligator to wrestle with at the North Pole. But were you to come across one, you could both wrestle it and win.

name: Horror Santa
description: He knows when you're awake...

name: Perfectly Legitimate Business Hat
description: aka Al Capwn

name: Fantasy Santa
description: He's an old school type of Santa. His interests are yuletide joy, boughs of holly, and figs.

name: Modern Military Santa
description: He sees you when you're sleeping.

name: DaVinci Copter
description: For inventors of all stripes.

name: Ninja Santa
description: Ninja Santa likes to sneak down people's chimneys and eat their cookies before Regular Santa gets there.

name: Mr. Chompers
description: Mr. Chompers will bet you 5 ROBUX that your entire head won't fit in his mouth...

name: LOL Santa
description: LOLOLOLOLOL - It's like Ho Ho Ho, but a bit more annoying.  That's what makes it hilarious!

name: Bubble Trouble
description: It's a bad idea to run and chew gum at the same time, unless you enjoy having gum stuck in your esophagus and being unable to breathe.

name: Wild West Santa
description: A cowboy is a man with guts and some reindeer.

name: Town and City Santa
description: Remember Christmas has nothing to do with consumerism and it is really all about family. Unless you are Town and City Santa. Then you are standing in line to return your gifts at Best Buy, 3pm on Christmas day.

name: Pirate Santa
description: If you be fool enough to be naughty, you'll be walkin the plank!

name: Pieface Jellyfreckles
description: Give a man a pie, he eats for a day. Teach a man to make pies and his house smells delicious forever!

name: Your Head, a Marshmallow Floating in Hot Chocolate
description: Mathematicians drink a ton of coffee. Young mathematicians drink a ton of hot chocolate. It's just the way of the world.

name: Snowman Face
description: Now all you need is a magic top hat.

name: Rudolph
description: He likes to pull heavy sleighs.

name: Swordpack
description: I swear, we're going to get around to making the DHG a feature... next year.

name: Orange Goggles
description: They are intended for high-speed double black diamond skiers, but they're also fun at parties.

name: NVG360 Hawkeyes
description: For you when absolutely must have 20/20 vision in the dark.

name: Subzero Ski Specs
description: Technically they are ski goggles, but they are really popular with snowboarders.

name: Elf Ears
description: Remember the fair folk? Before they left for the Grey Havens?

name: A Santa for All Seasons
description: Santa will find you where ever you are. If you are in a Town or City, Santa will find you. If you are in a Medieval fortress, Santa will find you. If you are on a Sci-Fi orbital battle platform, Santa will find you. If you are in a Ninja school, Santa will find you. If you are in R'lyeh, Santa will find you (though Santa hates that place). If you are on a Caribbean island, counting your buried treasure, Santa will find you. If you live inside a monster truck rally stadium, Santa will find you. If you live in the Wild American West? Yeah he'll find you there too. Serving in the military? Santa's gonna find you. And when Santa finds you, you'd BETTER have some milk and cookies waiting.

name: Goldenface
description: Neighbor to King Midas, Goldenface got his name when King Midas was swatting a fly and accidentally touched Goldenface's face.  Henceforth he was known as Goldenface.

name: 2010 Party Cap
description: I'm gunna party like it's 1999?  Wait that's not right....

name: 2010 New Year's Top Hat
description: Keep your new year classy with this snazzy cardboard top hat.

name: 2010 Roman Candle
description: Happy New Years!

name: Prankster
description: You didn't believe your mom when she said your face would freeze like that.  Oops!

name: 2010 Fireworks
description: Always remember, ROBLOX fireworks are fun, but real fireworks are dangerous. Don't play with real fireworks unless a responsible adult is present.

name: Newton
description: An apple hit his head and math came flying out. Released on Newton's birthday, 2010.

name: The Adventure of the Birthday Surprise
description: Surely a detective as great as Sherlock Holmes would have no surprises on his birthday.  Released on Sherlock Holmes Birthday 2010.

name: Bandage
description: Snitches get stitches!

name: Shaggy
description: It looks cooler on your guy, I promise.

name: ): Red Grind
description: ): is ROBLOXia's premier skateboard apparel brand. There's a Harvard business study that examines the wisdom of creating an unpronouncable brand name like ):. The main problem is that there is no way to spread awareness of the brand through word of mouth since no one can say ):. Bottom line: you have to be in the know to buy ):

name: The Bribe
description: Yeah. Being bribed is cool.

name: Classic Green Mohawk
description: Collectible hair?! That makes no sense!

name: Blue Katana of One Thousand Tears
description: So, often in the course / Of life's few fleeting years, / A single pleasure costs / The soul a thousand tears.

name: Crimson Destiny Turban
description: The Crimson Destiny seers are advisors to kings. Renown for their ability to pierce the misty viel of the future, their council is invaluable.

name: Ice Wizard
description: The moons are freezing but the stars are actually pretty insanely hot.

name: Benjamin Franklin
description: "Early to bed and early to rise makes a man healthy, wealthy, and wise." He would know.  This hat was released on 1/17/10 (Mr. Franklin's Birthday)

name: Green Laurel Wreath
description: These woods are lovely, dark and deep

name: Pwnda
description: You think you're tough? He eats Punji sticks for breakfast.

name: A Dark Presence
description: Conjurer's First Rule: Never summon anything you can't dismiss.

name: The Raven
description:
"Ghastly grim and ancient raven wandering from the nightly shore - Tell me what thy lordly name is on the Night's Plutonian shore!' Quoth the raven, `Nevermore.'" 

Released on 1/19/10- Poe's two hundred and first birthday.

name: Burning Otaku, the Firesouled
description: Fight fire with fire / Ending is near / Fight fire with fire / Bursting with fear

name: Fuchsia Fantastique
description: The Atom Bomb of hair cuts!

name: Optimist
description: Hey it's better than we thought! There's actually three glasses!

name: Dominus Empyreus
description: Quidquid latine dictum sit, altum sonatur...

name: Servant of the Secret Fire
description: They comb the world searching for Narya.

name: Crown of Om Nom Nom
description: Nom nom nom.

name: Noob Attack!
description: ZOMG GET IT OFF ME GET IT OFF MEEEEEEEE!

name: Embarrassed
description: Heh heh. Did you guys see me shoot myself with that rockets? Heh heh. No? Good, because it didn't happen.

name: Jade Katana of the Darkest Forest
description: "The career of a sage is of two kinds: He is either honored by all in the world, Like a flower waving its head, Or else he disappears into the silent forest." - Lao Tzu

name: Clown School Dropout
description: "You guys have held me back long enough, I'm going to clown school!"

name: Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Sword
description: In the aftermath of World War VII, isolated pockets of human survivors raided ruined government labs, looking specifically for these weapons. The Spec X program had been accelerated in the late 2120s as the prospect of an all out metahuman vs. machine war became increasingly likely. Prized for their ability to slice through viridian steel exoskeletons, the US was determined to find a substitute for the pure diamond required for the manufacture of the Beta models. Sapphire, while still exorbitantly expensive, allowed the army to produce blades that were 95% as effective as the Betas, at only 20% the cost.

name: Otterhead Shortsword
description: The pommel is an otter head. That's so weird!

name: The Arabian Nights
description: "Imagine a thousand thousand fireflies of every shape and color; Oh, that was Baghdad at night in those days."

name: A Very Special Monster
description: He has big big plans, but small small teeth.

name: Ronald McNinja
description: Would you like fries with your butt-whoopin'?

name: Snowman Headrow
description: Man - your actual head must be cold!

name: Santa's Formal Attire
description: "Do I have to?"  "Yes, Mr. Claus, you have to.  You only have to wear it once a year!"  "FINE!  But on Christmas I'm wearing my raggamuffin floppy cap."

name: Snowflake Shutter Shades
description: Because you're too fly for any other holiday gear.

name: Peppermint Headphones
description: Warning: These peppermint headphones only play holiday songs. Any attempt to play regular music with these headphones will lead the the permenant holidayization of your favorite songs.

name: Santa Chimney Top Hat
description: This novelty hat will be funny for years to come!  An instant classic!

name: Studded Trucker Hat
description: What I don't understand is how a trucker thinks he would be able to drive a truck in a hat without studs.

name: The Merry Avenger
description: His vengeance is swift and just..... and merry!

name: Annoying Elf: ReeseMcBlox
description: A jolly friend that gives you more speed,  but also gives your enemies more strength.

name: Glaurung the Greedy
description: All dragons are greedy.  Glaurung is no exception.

name: Disloyal Order of the Draphant
description: Should you trust a Draphant? No way.  They never forget and they've got some serious firepower.

name: Annoying Elf: Finsurf
description: Finsurf always has his mind on the numbers!  He might annoy you with some graphs, but he will definitely make sure every hit counts- by giving you extra strength!

name: Tropical Holiday Shoulder Bird
description: Mele Kalikimaka is the thing to say on a bright, Hawaiian, Christmas day!

name: 8-Bit Fedora
description: Because classy doesn't always mean more than 8-bits.

name: El Presidente
description: El Presidente is Presidente for life!

name: Deluxe Ninja Swordpack
description: I don't know about you, but sometimes, I need a lot of weapons. Like 2 swords, a sai, and some more swords in my hands....  This swordpack lets you carry more weapons than you could ever need!

name: Red Energy Sword
description: The last scientist who knew how to make energy swords passed away in a horrific energy sword accident.  Don't worry, he wasn't using his own energy swords (which function perfectly!).  He was testing a competitor's imitation sword when the energy suddenly exploded.  But this is not the end for energy swords!  They will live on.  How?  That's for another energy sword desciption.  How did we get these ones?  Duh - they were hidden in the scientist's basement.

name: Bluesteel Domino Crown
description: The classic shape in classic material. Classic.

name: Winter Bowler
description: Yeah it's snowing, so what?  I'm still gunna keep it classy. Deal.

name: Blue Spartan of the Future
description: This isn't Sparta!  This is future Sparta!

name: Da Money
description: I has it.

name: Blizzard Wand
description: Quit wishing for snow and make it happen...with this wand!    Also shoots icy blizzard balls at anyone near you.

name: Annoying Elf: Keith
description: These elves have a mind of their own!  Keith is no exception.  And he's got matches - I smell trouble...and hot dogs?

name: Dark Lord
description: He serves the Dark One, while at the same time fighting the Dark One's servants.  It is he who will be second in command when the Dark One returns.

name: Neon Trihawk
description: Because one centralized mohawk would be too easy.

name: The Dark Slayer
description: Doom awaits.

name: Venomshank
description: Because doesn't he deserve the most painful bloxxing possible?

name: Spectral Sword of Illusions
description: "Rainbows are visions, but only illusions / And Rainbows have nothing to hide"

name: New Years Crown 2012
description: Ring in the year with class and cardboard!

name: Samurai 3000 AD
description: Future samurai are robots - who would have guessed? Oh right...everyone.

name: Fashionable Contraption
description: Why should your contraptions look like contraptions when you can hide them in this fashionable hat!

name: Evil Henchman
description: 2nd in command....or so others think.

name: Crazy Crown
description: Crazy is the hair that wears the crown.

name: Noob Assist: Donut Dash
description: Breakfast is the most important meal of the day!

name: Dark Hooded Assassin of the All Seeing Order
description: He's from the all seeing order, but no one ever sees him coming.

name: Order of the Raven Hood
description: They take orders to follow only the darkest of commands.

name: Kronoboss
description: When you fight the ultimate evil and survive, you become the Kronoboss.

name: Seein' Stars + Stripes
description: "Freedom is never more than one generation away from extinction"

name: Azure Periastron Alpha
description: Only when two stars are at their closest point, can the material for this sword be collected, so they are extremely rare, and depending on which stars are orbiting one another they are different colors.  One thing is sure, they spell doom for anyone who comes near. First in a series!

name: Dark Alien Hatchling
description: When you see this egg - you better run!  As soon as the alien hatches, it's too late!

name: Yachting Fedora
description: Because a captain's hat is so cliche and new money.

name: Pocket Top Hat
description: Because pants pockets are so 5 years ago.

name: Dark Minion
description: Not a guy I'd want to meet in a dark alley.

name: Knights of the Seventh Sanctum : Dual Duel Axes
description: You're dueling.  Your opponent has an axe... but you have two!  Wield the unholy relics of the Seventh Sanctum and no one else stands a chance... unless they have these axes too.  But how likely is that?

name: Trololololo Wand
description: Turn your enemies into trolls!  They'll be slower and very confused!

name: The Devil's Cowboy
description: He's seen things no living man should have ever seen.

name: Dragon's Breath Potion
description: Yeah this does exactly what you think it does. Drink it and you can shoot flames at anything and everything!

name: Year of the Dragon Lantern
description: Light the lantern to invoke the protection of the ancient dragon spirits.  If anyone is foolish enough to attack you while you are surrounded by dragon spirits, well then maybe they get what they deserve.

name: Magic Lamp
description: Rub the lamp, and a genie appears to grant you a wish.

name: Dagger of Shattered Dimensions
description: At first stab, it appears to be an ordinary dagger. But one quick press of the 'Q' key proves it to be something quite different.  Something that shatters dimensions.  Particularly the dimension of time.

name: Ninja Master: Dojo of Doom
description: The stealth ninjas from the dojo of doom, know exactly what you're doing.  By the time you know what they're doing, it's too late.

name: Ninja Necktie
description: When you wonder where the ninja is, you know he's right behind you.

name: Sinister Branches
description: I threw a wish in the well / Don't ask me, I'll never tell / I looked to you as it fell / And now you're in my way

name: Slithering Slayer
description: He sneaks by stealthly to steal your swagger.... and weapons.

name: Dark Horns of Pwnage
description: Pwnin' ain't easy.

name: Wanderer Vampire Slayer
description: We kind of envision a creepy tall guy with mutton chops wearing this.

name: Steelshanks Armament
description: Pirates don't fight fair. They bring guns to sword fights.

name: Captain Steelshanks Recruiting Staff
description: Captain Steelshanks is recruiting a crew for his vessel, the Ironsides.  Don't want to be a pirate?  Too bad.

name: Creepy Zombie Monkey
description: Captain Steelshank's semi-loyal companion.

name: Heartbreaker
description: "You're a heart breaker / dream maker, love taker / Don't you mess around with me!"

name: Valentine's Day 2012 Cap
description: "I poured my heart out... it evaporated."

name: Red Sparkle Time Fedora
description: In this hat it's Sparkle Time all the time.  What is Sparkle Time? Well it's better than peanut butter jelly time, that's for sure.

name: Lightning Orb
description: Summon lightning to stun your enemies!

name: Zombie Fiend
description: Your brain is his favorite flavor...brain flavored.  Wonder why that never caught on as a flavor....

name: Elven Prince
description: He is small, but mighty.  His people are counting on him and there is no turning back.  Failure is not an option.

name: Dragon Slayers Sword and Shield
description: Protecting the people from dragons is its primary goal.  Whatever else you do with it is your own business.

name: Wraith's Screech Potion
description: His scream pierces all that come near him.

name: Dark Assassin
description: In the dark of the night, he lurks, waiting.

name: The Axe of Undoing: A Walmart Exclusive
description: This axe will be the undoing of everything!  Awarded when you redeemed a card from Walmart in March, 2012.

name: Grimgold Periastron Beta
description: The sword men use to fight bears... in space.

name: Panda Knit
description: There's panda inside!

name: Magma Realm Mage
description: The magma cannot be tamed, but its flows can be guided....

name: Decorated Soldier
description: "I am a soldier, I fight where I am told, and I win where I fight."

name: Valkyrie 3000
description: In the future - all robots wear valkyries.  The future doesn't make sense.

name: Squid Overlord
description: He lost some legs, but you should see the other guy.

name: Glory Launcher 2012
description: With this heat seeking missile launcher, your foes don't stand a chance.

name: Gravitron 3000
description: Toss this to negate gravity for everyone but yourself.

name: Frozen Horns of the Frigid Planes
description: Banishment was meant to extinguish his fire, but it only made it burn colder.

name: Scary Hood
description: This is scary...very scary!

name: The Luck O' the Irish
description: You just got McPwned.

name: Irish Gentleman
description: For the great Gaels of Ireland / Are the men that God made mad, / For all their wars are merry, / And all their songs are sad.

name: Crimson Catseye Top Hat
description: A young ambitious haberdasher acquired the Crimson Catseye from Haunted Hill on a crazy dare. He then became known as Catseye Speaker and created these hats to commemorate that night.

name: Captain Greenshanks the Lucky
description: Greenshanks never had the biggest ships, but it seemed that luck was always on his side.

name: Emerald Crystal Circlet
description: These enchanted emerald crystals are sure to bring you luck!

name: St. Patrick's Day 2012
description: Celebrate St. Patrick's day in style!

name: Submarine Commander
description: Everyone on a sub carries weapons.  When he says fire the nuke, you do it.

name: Leprechaun Friend
description: You're lucky he likes you.

name: Rubber Chicken Wand
description: Your enemy is coming at you fast and furious with the Darkheart Sword.  What do you do?  Turn the sword into a rubber chicken of course.

name: Monster Friend
description: Monster friend or monster fiend?

name: The Reckoner
description: The reckoning is coming in the form of one man.

name: Hedgehog Friend
description: Why can't they just share the hedge?

name: Charles Babbage Fabergé Egg
description: Individuals this far ahead of their time are vanishingly rare.

name: Chaos Canyon Sugar Egg
description: This highly collectible commemorative egg recalls that *other* classic ROBLOX level, the one that was never quite as popular as Crossroads.

name: Crossroads Sugar Egg
description: Find this highly collectible commemorative Crossroads egg and brag about it to your friends. There's always a showdown at the Crossroads!

name: Eggcognito Egg
description: Find the Eggcognito egg when he is pretending to be you. He usually disguises himself with a hat that you are wearing along with a fake mustache and glasses.

name: Aqueous Egg of River Riding
description: Don't go chasing waterfalls / Please stick to the rivers and the lakes that you're used to

name: Desert Airbreather
description: To survive in this wind blown dust bowl of a land, you must never uncover your mouth.

name: Steampunk Sweetheart Top Hat
description: A machine cannot love.  But I sure love this hat!

name: Thrift Shop Fedora
description: You just popped some tags... and it was awesome!

name: Red Illusion Fedora
description: Is that a bow or just some well placed thread? I'll never tell.

name: Toothy Cap
description: No one will be able to bite your style in this cap.

name: Korblox - Fallen's Spine Blade
description: In the heat of battle, when the weapon fails him, a true Korblox warrior is not afraid of ripping his spine apart and slashing through his adversaries.

name: Dr. Crazybot
description: I don't know where he got his degree but I don't want him getting within two feet of me with a scalpel.

name: Bolt Biter
description: He can smell those delicious bolts you have hidden in your car... and he wants to eat them.

name: Donald P Sullivan - Gold Edition
description: Didn't think everybody's favorite robot could get any fancier? You were wrong.

name: Radioactive Robot
description: A couple years in a chemical dumping ground would make you radioactive too.

name: Redspybot
description: How could something so conspicuous be a spy?

name: Captain Bluesteel
description: Sailing the stormy seas of ROBLOX with steely resolve.

name: Double Damage Frog
description: Throw this double damage frog at your foes. If it hits them, his poison rubs off on them and they turn blue for twenty seconds!  Any damage you do to them during this time is doubly effective!

name: Fiesta Sombrero
description: Let's party!

name: Midnight Top Hat
description: "Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered weak and weary..."

name: Icy Depths Fedora
description: What lies below? Nobody knows until you crack the ice!

name: Grumpy Robot
description: Safe to say he's having a rough week at the factory.

name: Blox U Grad Cap 2013
description: I'm majoring in building!

name: ROBLOX World Tour Lightning Guitar
description: ROBLOX is kicking off our world tour and it's gunna be loud!  This slammin' lighting guitar will send lightning at anyone nearby is you can play the notes just right.

name: ROBLOX World Tour Hot Air Balloon
description: This thing will take you on a world tour of ROBLOX in 80 days or less!  Not really, but it will fly you and a buddy around the level and make you look awesome in your avatar thumbnail.  Our first personal transport vehicle for two!

name: Rosey Smile
description: I make this face when I think about pizza.

name: Ogre Friend
description: Friend or foe?  You be the judge!

name: Off the Chain Style

name: I, LOLRUS
description:
YOKOHAMA (Kyodo) Minazo, Japan's largest seal, died this week having charmed visitors for 10 1/2 years at Enoshima Aquarium in Fujisawa, Kanagawa Prefecture, aquarium officials said.

The 11-year-old male, 4.5-meters long and weighing about 2 tons, was the largest seal ever raised by a Japanese aquarium. The animal died Tuesday after its appetite began to rapidly weaken the day before, officials said. The cause of death was not immediately known.

Minazo was brought to Japan from Uruguay in 1995. The seal soon mastered a variety of comical feats, including a popular stunt in which he held a bucket with one flipper while sticking out his tongue.

Minazo quickly rose to stardom at the aquarium, where his three shows a day proved a hit with visitors.

The aquarium has set up a space in front of Minazo's water tank to allow visitors to leave flowers in Minazo's memory, the officials said.

name: King of New Calclica

name: Umadbro?
description: Umad that you don't have this tie?

description: You're epic and you've got the tie to prove it!

name: Ultimate Slide Skateboard
description: Time to show off as the coolest kid on the block!

name: Emerald Crescent Samurai
description: All the other samurai are green with envy.

description: It's ever so slightly different than the one we sold for 1 tix, altered to fit on Bling Boy.

description: When I asked for a summer hat, this isn't exactly what I meant! Lol

name: Rainbow Sunglasses
description: Stay cool in these hot shades!

description: You were victorious over a dinosaur!  Awesome! Oh...you got it at the science museum? I guess that's cool too....

description: Like the lone ranger but with you know...more space! No not literal space - like outerspace! I get the feeling you're being deliberately obtuse...

description: The typical Korblox King does not reign for long.  The King must fight to keep the position against anyone who dares to challenge him for the kingdom.

name: Dare Devil
description: "I know guys in my hometown that drive by feel and sound."- Evel Knievel

name: Kitty Monster

name: Paranoia Attack
description: He's paranoid so you don't have to be.

name: Elven Princess
description: She is small, but mighty.  Her people are counting on her and there is no turning back.  Failure is not an option.

name: ): Green Sidewinder
description: Don't look back. You're not going that way.

name: Dominus Rex
description: A mari usque ad mare.

name: Tasteless Bow Tie
description: You've got style, you've got grace, but no taste.

name: Gilded Wings of Glory
description: These fabulous wings aren't made of wax! Go ahead- fly as close to the sun as you like! They're the genuine article!

name: Sad Clown
description: No one likes a clown who reminds them of why they hate ice-cream-truck music.

name: Beach House Fedora
description: Perfect for role playing at a beach house... or just walking around your little seaside town.

name: Bombastic Katana
description: *Bombastic first aid kit not included.

description: On this episode of When Animals Attack: This tiger is hungry and ready to rumble!

name: Glorious Purple Party Queen
description: Used to being on the road, / Crazy nights and playing shows.

name: Black Sparkle Time Fedora
description: Let your dim light sparkle.

name: Bluesteel Bucket
description: I HAZ A BLUESTEEL BUCKET.

name: Universal Fedora
description: Perfect for whatever planet you might turn out to be on.

name: Midnight Commando
description: He commands the night watch.  He commands them all.

name: Masked Hood of the Midsummers Night Rogue
description: The summer air is hot like his temper.

name: Blue Sleepy Owl
description: "What is the hurry? It's pretty early / It's okay, we'll take our time"

name: Green Trance
description: Man, I love creamsicles.  I just ate a lot of them. I'm feeling a bit strange actually.

name: Orange Trance
description: Man, I love creamsicles.

name: Purple Trance
description: Man, I love creamsicles.  I just ate a lot of them. I'm feeling a bit strange actually.  Do you see that? It's magical. Like all the good things about the universe morphed into a giant creamsicle of joy. This is pretty much the best day of my life.

name: Neon Rainbow Phoenix
description: Your guardian phoenix follows you and protects you by shooting different color fireballs at your foes. Each hit does 25 damage!

name: Neon Pink Trihawk
description: Because even two mohawks would be too easy.

name: American Eagle
description: On the wings of freedom, he flies.

name: For the Ages: William Shakespeare
description: "We know what we are, but know not what we may be."

name: Azure Dragon's Magic Slayer
description: Click to deal your foes 16 to 22 points of damage.  If you successfully blox your foe, they become a  skeleton! Click and hold to charge a special attack which creates a magic purple portal in front of you. It'll then suck in objects and players and instantly kill them if they come in contact with it!

name: CW Ultimate: Emerald Entropy
description: They're playin' your jam - "Overseer Overture".

name: Bucket of the Sea
description: Pirates thought this bucket was perfect for clearing out the Bilge.  Then one day, an apprentice dropped the bucket overboard.  Now it's the perfect hat!

name: Cantaloupe Samurai
description: He is always throwing his enemies for a loop!

name: Breakfast Shades
description: I eat problems for breakfast...so I can use my breakfast to make cool outfits.

name: Citrine Vision Visor
description: "Forward's the only way to go"

name: 1337 Gaming Headset
description: I'm gunna go pro. Too MLG for you.

name: Blizzard Striker
description: Everywhere you go, the freezing snow follows. Anyone who gets close to you while you are wielding this sword will lose health due to the pain of being near your icy cold weapon.  Click to slash at your enemies, dealing around 15 damage per hit. There is a 20% chance your enemy will freeze into a block of ice for 15 seconds. This disables control over his character, making him unable to move and very vulnerable to your frozen attacks.  Let it go, indeed!

name: Horns of the Magmawrath
description: Don't call him a hothead. It was only funny the first 1000 times.

name: Mildly Irritated Face
description: Oh no, you don't want to see him when he gets mad.  Imagine this times 1000.  His eyes turn red. Note - eyes are super large and may not work with some other ROBLOX items.

name: Omega Rainbow Bowler
description: As a sophisticated citizen of the future, you know that a hat is a must for a time traveling journey.

name: Overseer Overlord
description: The Overseers have many ranks so that no one ever knows exactly who is in charge.  Chaos is their leadership philosophy.  May the strongest Overseer win.

name: Overseer Hooded Cloak
description: "I let go. Lost in oblivion. Dark and silent and complete. I found freedom."

name: Korblox Shoulder Pauldrons
description: Mean and bad as the day is long, the Korblox warriors are constantly inventing new ways to punish their foes. This armor reflects these sensibilities.

name: CW Ultimate: Wulfinite Will
description: They're playin' your jam - "Gusmanak Grunge".

name: Merely's Bluesteel Hoverboard
description: Merely is basically the Tony Hawk of hoverboarding.

name: Overseer Crossbow
description: Click and hold to rapidly fire arrows at your foes. Hit the 'Q' key to activate the Overseer's Menacing Arrow. Once fired, a massively sized Overseer Eye will magically replace the arrow and explode into hundreds of tiny eyes, which will shoot in all directions!

name: Omega Rainbow Sword
description: The power of all future rainbows is at your finger tips. Click to slash, dealing 18 to 22 damage per hit. Double click to dash forward with the speed of a magical rainbow!

name: From the Vault: Alpaca Plushie
description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - this giant alpaca! Defaultio's alpaca makes many animal noises and when you drop it, it grows intimidatingly large.

description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - an angry alligator! ZolarKeth's alligator launches into the air and retrieves a basketball from the nether. The alligator then follows the player at a maximum speed of seventeen.

name: From the Vault: Kawaii Cat
description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - this kawaii cat! Rukiryo's cat will follow you around and listen to your commands. You can tell it to follow and to stay. There's also a special word to make it evolve. Will you find it?

name: From the Vault: Dozens of Dinosaurs
description: From the vault of interns past, ROBLOX brings you - dozens of dinosaurs! Sharksie's pack of dinos spawns 14 plushie dinos for you to enjoy.

name: Cobolt Lightning Pauldrons
description: Like a bolt from the blue, they strike surprisingly and suddenly.

name: Bombastic Boa
description: As bold and dangerous about the deal you're about to make.

name: Crimson Shaggy
description: Because Neon Pink Shaggys don't know how to be bold.

name: Archduke of the Federation
description: The Wars of Reunification are complete. The Federation is whole once more. All of creation is yours.

name: Violet Princess of the North
description: Long live the princess! May she be wise enough to one day become the queen.

name: Sapphire Crystal Circlet
description: True blue gems for you.

name: Pig with Aviators
description: They call me Bacon. That's Mr. Bacon to you!

name: Lost Boy of Summer Hair
description:
"Can I sell this sunrise, in return for a sunset? yeah.. /
Can I just be here one more day, until my sunburn fades away?"

name: Ceremonial Guard of the Duke of the Federation
description: Death before dishonor.

name: Dethroned Ruler of the Universe
description: He will stop at nothing to reclaim the throne. Worlds will burn.

name: Evil Duck Roped
description: The most sinister roped yet!  Hit the 'H' key to make it quack!  Hit 'Q' to make it rain ducks.

name: Omega Rainbow Fedora
description: Time is on your side. Because you can travel through it. Wherever you'd like.

name: Spider Web Collar
description: Carefully spun, stylishly worn.

name: Spider Slasher
description: Click to slash double-click to lunge and do 12 damage. When you lunge, you also shoot a web in the the direction of your cursor. If it hits somebody, their speed is reduced to 6 for a few seconds, giving you an opportunity to catch up to them. While slashing your enemy with the sword, there is a 30% chance of poisoning them!

name: Zombie Doge
description: So undead. Much brains. Wow.

name: Dark Skeleton Crown
description: To rule the undead, to lead those not living.

name: Vampire Sunglasses
description: I don't know when you'd need these... because vampires can't go outside while the sun is shining. Nevertheless, these are cool as anything.

name: Mysterious Witch Pumpkin
description: The potion backfired and now she was destined to be the pumpkin head.

name: Monster Bow Tie
description: Pretty much the only thing you can wear to the monster mash ball.

name: WC Ultimates: Pink Diamond Distraction
description: They're playing your jam, "Big Beautiful Distraction". This item came out of the Musical Gift of Pink Diamonds on February 12th, 2016.

name: Magic Wizard Owl
description: Why are owls magical - hoo knows? Hoo hoo.

name: Dual Monster Axes
description: Sling these at your foes to do some major damage! You'll do 12 to 17 damage when you slash you foes and 25 points on double slash!

name: Neon Pink Pirate Patch
description: Sailing the seas of adventure in colorful style!

description: Click to slash, dealing 14 to 17 damage. With each slash you'll unlock the ancient power of the Pharaoh's Guard and have a chance at preforming a secret attack or enjoying a hidden power up!

Never look backwards... you're not going that way.

description: What's cooler than being cool? Chilled.

description: This peppermint winter is so sugar sweet.

name: Sneaky Green-Eyed Snake

name: Teal Rock Star Smile
description:
"So you wanna be a rock superstar? /
And live large, a big house, 5 cars, you're in charge"

name: Dual Spec Gamma Biograft Energy Sword

name: Ceremonial Guard of the Archduke of the Federation

name: Fire Flash Shades

name: Overseer Armor Pauldrons

name: GoldLika: Troll
description: Like a troll...

name: Green Glowing Eyes
description: You're watching Netflix videos- just chillin' on a typical Friday night. You hear a sound. You look out the window. You see these green glowing eyes and nothing else.  You go outside to inspect the situation. You approach the figure. It is your best friend. He bought this face just to mess with you. Friends are weird.

name: Bacon Face
description: I'm bacon you to cut these puns out.

name: Lightning Cobalt Pauldrons
description: Like a bolt from the blue, they strike suddenly and surprisingly.

name: Friendly Trusting Smile

name: Crimsonwrath: The Red Wrath

When using, your speed is boosted 4 points making you slightly faster, enough to trail behind enemies which flee. Each kill, the sword gets even stronger for a few seconds! When killed, enemies turn into flaming transparent red ghosts which quickly fade away up into the sky!

name: Red Serious Scar Face
description: He's seen things you couldn't even imagine. Recently. You know that 'cause the scar is still red.

name: Gritty Bombo

name: Green Drool Angry Zombie

name: Metal Feathers of Fate

name: Ermine Cloak
description: Royalty is attitude.

name: Wings of Liberty
description: "Where liberty dwells, there is my country."

name: Lady Liberty Headphones
description: Hello there lovers of liberty! Let freedom ring! In your ears!

name: Real Flaming Hot Stunnas
description: I got so much fire... it's like a furnace up in here.

name: Noob Attack: Amerilaser Ambush
description: How'd a noob get an Amerilaser? Somebody left the door unlocked again...

description: Because Tix Shaggy lacks passion.

name: Omega Rainbow Top Hat
description: Puttin' on the ritz... future edition.

name: Red Crown of Ozymandias
description:
I met a traveller from an antique land /
Who said: Two vast and trunkless legs of stone /
Stand in the desert. Near them on the sand, /
Half sunk, a shatter'd visage lies, whose frown /
And wrinkled lip and sneer of cold command /
Tell that its sculptor well those passions read /
Which yet survive, stamp'd on these lifeless things, /
The hand that mock'd them and the heart that fed. /
And on the pedestal these words appear: /
"My name is Ozymandias, king of kings: /
Look on my works, ye Mighty, and despair!" /
Nothing beside remains: round the decay /
Of that colossal wreck, boundless and bare, /
The lone sands stretch far away.

name: Dark Cerulean Crown of Ozymandias
description:
In Egypt's sandy silence, all alone, /
Stands a gigantic Leg, which far off throws /
The only shadow that the Desert knows: /
"I am great OZYMANDIAS," saith the stone, /
"The King of Kings; this mighty City shows /
"The wonders of my hand." The City's gone, /
Nought but the Leg remaining to disclose /
The site of this forgotten Babylon. /
We wonder, and some Hunter may express /
Wonder like ours, when thro' the wilderness /
Where London stood, holding the Wolf in chace, /
He meets some fragments huge, and stops to guess /
What powerful but unrecorded race /
Once dwelt in that annihilated place.

description: ROBLOX Brings You...ROBLOX Brings You...ROBLOX Brings You... the most awesome electric guitar ever known to Robloxians!

name: General Protection Fault
description: General Protection Fault is a time-traveling war criminal from the future. He's wanted on 14 worlds for various heinous acts. Despite the fact that surveilance is ubiquitious in many sectors of the galaxy, no one living has ever seen his real face.

description: Our summer intern Socom1880 has seen terrible things, and now he has to wear this mask to hide his ruined face from the world.

name: Robber Baron Top Hat
description: With this top hat, you'll be the shooting image of Leland Stanford.

name: Outlawed Vampumatiger Hybrid
description: On a remote planet, a crazy scientist mixed DNA from humans, pumas, tigers, and vampires to create this freak of nature. With the speed of a puma, the dexterity of a tiger, and the insaitable bloodlust of vampires the hybrids represented an existential threat to civilized worlds. Over the course of several decades they were hunted to extinction. Or were they...

name: Tokyokhaos Giraffe
description: Tokyokhaos was Robloxia's most popular anime cartoon, before it got shutdown for causing seizures in children. The Giraffe is Go-playing master with the ability to see into the future. He works a day job at the zoo, but dreams of something bigger.

name: Iceworld Smuggler
description: The Iceworld Smugglers work the dark triangle that is made up of three destinations along the Outer Rim. Melange from Rakis travels to the frozen world, Crystalis, to trade for weapons-grade Ice-Nine, which is then smuggled to Mecatol Rex. The weapons are traded for priceless alien artifacts, which are conveyed back to Rakis. At each point in the journey, the smugglers take extreme risk and make incredible fortunes.

name: Spec Beta Biograft Energy Sword
description: In 2113, decades after the initial release of the hugely successful Spec Alpha biograft energy weapons, the US government began research on a top-secret upgrade. The breakthrough was to use artificial diamonds to forge the blade itself, rather that carbon nanofibers. The new weapon was very effective, but obscenely expensive. Only a hundred were ever made.

name: Vlad the Impaler, IV

name: Classicx89's Stylin' Intern Shades

You order lattes made with free trade soy milk. You pretend to like poetry accompanied by bongos. You are everything that is wrong with this country.
